{"lemma":"طِفْلِ","slug":"طِفْلِ","root":"ط.ف.ل","root_slug":"ط-ف-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ط-ف-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"طِفْل","root":"طفل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":4},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n26827","n26831","n26832","n26833","n26834"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B7%D9%90%D9%81%D9%92%D9%84%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"child (a minor)","examples":[{"text":"الطِّفْلُ فِي الْمَغَارَة وَأُمُّهُ مَرْيَم وَجْهَانِ يَبْكِيَانِ\nيَبْكِيَانِ لِأَجْلِ مَنْ تَشَرَّدُوا\nلِأَجْلِ أَطْفَالٍ بِلَا مَنَازِل","english":"The child and his mother Maryam in the cave, two faces crying.\nCrying for those made homeless,\nFor children without houses."}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"children (a minor)","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"وَنُقِرُّ فِي الْأَرْحَامِ مَا نَشَاءُ إِلَى أَجَلٍ مُسَمًّى ثُمَّ نُخْرِجُكُمْ طِفْلًا ثُمَّ لِتَبْلُغُوا أَشُدَّكُمْ","english":"˹Then˺ We settle whatever ˹embryo˺ We will in the womb for an appointed term, then bring you forth as infants, so that ye may reach your prime. Some of you ˹may˺ die ˹young˺, while others are left to reach the most feeble stage of life so that they may know nothing after having known much."},{"text":"أَوِ الطِّفْلِ الَّذِينَ لَمْ يَظْهَرُوا عَلَى عَوْرَاتِ النِّسَاءِ","english":"or children who are still unaware of women’s nakedness."}]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/tˤifl/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n26827","headword_ar":"طَفُلَ","root":"Tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TafaAlapN","text_ar":"طَفَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TufuwlapN","text_ar":"طُفُولَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(anything)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[as though resembling a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tifol","text_ar":"طِفْل"},{"kind":"text","text":";] (K, TA;) syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raxuSa","text_ar":"رَخُصَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafalat","text_ar":"طَفَلَت"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a she-camel: see 2. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafala","text_ar":"طَفَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TufuwlN","text_ar":"طُفُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a man, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He entered upon the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"time called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafal","text_ar":"طَفَل"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) which has two contr. meanings; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ATfl","text_ar":"اطفل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafalati","text_ar":"طَفَلَتِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~amosu","text_ar":"الشَّمْسُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun rose:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) so says Fr in his “ Nawádir. ” (O.) ―         -b4-  And, (O, K,) accord. to Zj, (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun became red on the occasion of setting;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTofalat","text_ar":"اَطْفَلَت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (O, K:) thus the former has two contr. meanings: (K:) and"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1860},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al$~amos","text_ar":"الشَّمْس"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tf~lt","text_ar":"طفّلت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tf~lt liloguruwbi","text_ar":"طفّلت لِلْغُرُوبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTofiylN","text_ar":"تَطْفِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sun inclined to setting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"approached the setting;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafalat","text_ar":"طَفَلَت"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TufuwlN","text_ar":"طُفُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafalati AlHumuru AlEu$oba","text_ar":"طَفَلَتِ الحُمُرُ العُشْبَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The asses depastured the herbs so as to raise the dust upon them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn- 'Abbád, O.)       -A4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafila Aln~abotu","text_ar":"طَفِلَ النَّبْتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Ibn-' Abbád, O, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tufila","text_ar":"طُفِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Ibn-' Abbád, O, TA;) or, accord. to the K, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tuf~ila","text_ar":"طُفِّلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTofiylN","text_ar":"تَطْفِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The herbage became soiled by dust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn-' Abbád, O, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and thereby marred,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"injured."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ibn- ' Abbád, O, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","O","S"]},{"entry_id":"n26831","headword_ar":"طَفْلٌ","root":"Tfl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K;) applied to anything, (K:) fem, with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, O, K;) applied to a girl, or young woman, (S,) or to a woman: (O:) and pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifaAlN","text_ar":"طِفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TufuwlN","text_ar":"طُفُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K.) One says"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"banaAnN TafolN","text_ar":"بَنَانٌ طَفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender, fingers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ends of fingers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; this being allowable, though"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bnAn","text_ar":"بنان"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a [kind of] pl. and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tfl","text_ar":"طفل"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a sing., because every pl. [of the kind] that differs not from its sing. save in the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[affixed to the latter] is made sing. and masc. [as well as fem.]: and therefore Homeyd says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"falam~aA ka$afona All~ibosa Eanohu masaHonahu\n                      \n                     \n                        biA^aToraAfi TafolK zaAna gayolFA muwa$~amFA"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And when they"},{"kind":"text","text":"(referring to females)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"removed from over him the clothing, they wiped him with the extremities of soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender, fingers, that adorned a plump fore arm, tattooed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA^aToraAfi binaAnK TafolK","text_ar":"بِاَطْرَافِ بِنَانٍ طَفْلٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.)       -A2-  Also ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Fullers' earth, which is used for scouring cloths, and is sometimes used in the bath, instead of soap;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a certain yellow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yellowish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and sometimes"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"white,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whitish,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earth, well known in Egypt, with which cloths are dyed"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or rather"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scoured"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bayoluwnN","text_ar":"بَيْلُونٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Esh-Shiháb El- ' Ajamee, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bln","text_ar":"بلن"},{"kind":"text","text":".)"}],"source_refs":["K","S","O"]},{"entry_id":"n26832","headword_ar":"طِفْلٌ","root":"Tfl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A young one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"youngling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, K, *) of anything, (K,) [or] of a human being and of a beast: (Msb:) or (K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a new-born child,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young infant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a young one,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"young,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of any wild animal: (S, O, K:) or it is applied to"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a child until he discriminates;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb, TA;) after which he is called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiY~","text_ar":"صَبِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; thus some say, (Msb,) [and] thus says El-Munáwee: (TA:) or, accord. to Az, (Msb, TA,) on the authority of AHeyth, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a child from the time of his birth"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"until he attains to puberty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA:) fem."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolapN","text_ar":"طِفْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Zj, Mgh, Msb, TA:) and pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTofaAlN","text_ar":"اَطْفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Zj, S, O, Msb, TA:) but"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolN","text_ar":"طِفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used as fem., (Zj, Mgh, O, Msb, TA,) and dual, (Zj, TA,) and pl., (Zj, S, O, Msb, TA,) occurring as pl. in the Kur xxiv. 31, (S, O, Msb,) and [xxii. 5 and] xl. 69: (Zj, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifoyalN","text_ar":"طِفْيَلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolN","text_ar":"طِفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) used in this sense by a rájiz; but accord. to some, by poetic license, for the dim. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TufayolN","text_ar":"طُفَيْلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any part or portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"of anything, whether a substance or an accident: (K, TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTofaAlN","text_ar":"اَطْفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": whence they say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tifolu Alham~i","text_ar":"طِفْلُ الهَمِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHub~i","text_ar":"الحُبِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The portion of anxiety"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of love"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b3-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A falling spark"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqoT","text_ar":"سِقْط"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaT","text_ar":"سَقَط"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) of fire: (M, K, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a live coal:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fire when just struck;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolapN","text_ar":"طِفْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, TA: [but this latter is the n. un.:]) and the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aTofaAlN","text_ar":"اَطْفَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taTaAyarato A^aTofaAlu","text_ar":"تَطَايَرَتْ اَطْفَالُ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aAri","text_ar":"النَّارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The sparks of the fire"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became scattered"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b4-  (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Small clouds:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in a verse of Aboo-Dhu-eyb. (TA.) ―         -b5-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An object of want:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small object of want."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa yasoEaY fiY A^aTofaAli AlHawaAy^iji","text_ar":"هُوَ يَسْعَى فِى اَطْفَالِ الحَوَايِجِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. [(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He labours in the accomplishment of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"small objects of want."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.)       -A2-  (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"first part thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, TA.) ―         -b2-  And (assumed tropical:)  The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sun when near to the setting."},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Msb","S","O","TA","Mgh","Zj","M","A"]},{"entry_id":"n26833","headword_ar":"طَفَلٌ","root":"Tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tufuwliy~apN","text_ar":"طُفُولِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"period"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"next"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"after sunrise:"},{"kind":"text","text":"from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TifolN","text_ar":"طِفْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying “ a young one ” or “ youngling: ” (O:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafalu AlgadaApi","text_ar":"طَفَلُ الغَدَاةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the period from that when the sun is about to rise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appear, until its light has ascendancy over the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the sun is about to rise,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appear, and has not yet ascendancy in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon, the earth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Er-Rághib, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the period from the rising,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"appearing, of the sun, until its having ascendancy"},{"kind":"text","text":"[for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilaY A@sotikomaAlihaA","text_ar":"اـِلَى ا@سْتِكْمَالِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in a copy of the M, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstkmAnhA","text_ar":"استكمانها"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AstknAnhA","text_ar":"استكنانها"},{"kind":"text","text":"in different copies of the K, I read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlY A@sotimokaAnihaA","text_ar":"الى ا@سْتِمْكَانِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", agreeably with the explanation in the the T and with that of Er-Rághib, in both of which the verb used is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yasotamokin","text_ar":"يَسْتَمْكِن"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon, the earth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) And (O) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"period after"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaSor","text_ar":"عَصْر"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when the sun inclines to the setting:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafalu AlEa$iY~i","text_ar":"طَفَلُ العَشِىِّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the last part of the afternoon, at sunset,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the time of the sun's becoming yellow, when it is about to set."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^atayotuhu TafalFA","text_ar":"اَتَيْتُهُ طَفَلًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I came to him at one of the periods termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafal","text_ar":"طَفَل"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) ―         -b3-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"coming of the night with its darkness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"darkness"},{"kind":"text","text":"itself. (O, K.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Rain:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tafalu Alv~uray~aA","text_ar":"طَفَلُ الثُّرَيَّا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The rain"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the auroral setting"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the Pleiades"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) [Or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A shower"},{"kind":"text","text":"of rain: for] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waqaEato A^aTofaAlu AlwasomiY~i","text_ar":"وَقَعَتْ اَطْفَالُ الوَسْمِىِّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The showers of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"[rain called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wsmY~","text_ar":"وسمىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fell:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaAdahu TafalN mino maTarK","text_ar":"جَادَهُ طَفَلٌ مِنْ مَطَرٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A shower of rain descended copiously upon him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (A, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyHN TafalN","text_ar":"رِيحٌ طَفَلٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A wind that blows gently,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"softly."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["O","T","TA","S","K"]},{"entry_id":"n26834","headword_ar":"طَفِلٌ","root":"Tfl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"Herbage"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that does not become tall"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}